{
  "stem": "26142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those were what the Hungarians called [NON-ENGLISH], detectives or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had a list.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had a list.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And gendarmes and police were bringing out, bringing in more and more families into the synagogue from the entire-- entire community.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was such a shock that we were-- brains stopped-- stopped thinking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do, what to think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Fortunately for us, they brought in my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was Moshe, his wife, and the two children, they brought in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They brought up my-- my uncles and other family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we knew each other in a small community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had 135 families.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You knew--- you knew every family, even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this notar, the local notar-- he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- this was really a miracle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said-- he looked at the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said that Abraham Jakuvobics is not on the list, because he is 75 years of age.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I told you that this was wrongly listed or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was-- his-- his-- [INAUDIBLE] under his-- he had the authority.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he said to my mother and my father, you go back to your house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And soldiers-- he ordered soldiers to escort them back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They go back to their house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and it turned out-- it turned out that out of the 135 families, they had 18, 17 or 18 people that were listed above 75 years of age, that those people were spared.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were left-- left-- left home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As soon as we-- we saw our parents, are-- are out, the anxiety was lessened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "At least-- at least, for us, I mean, my brother Tsvi-- I was 21.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and-- and he was 3-- 32, 33.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
